{"body": "This changes the order of insert/update/destroy actions!!\r\n\r\nwith this fix: first insert/update records and after all of this is done, destroy records marked for destruction. \r\nbefore: insert/update/destroy record by record\r\n\r\nthis causes a problem when you have a unique index on your table. If any update/insert has the same values on the unique index then a record marked for destruction, you get an unique index errors.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/14622316", "created_at": "2013-03-08T14:17:58Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3329#issuecomment-14622316", "updated_at": "2013-03-08T14:17:58Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3329, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/aka47", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/cbd4648e4cd1dd7e8737c8ca91fcda02?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F970627414218ccff3497cb7a784288f5.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/received_events", "gravatar_id": "cbd4648e4cd1dd7e8737c8ca91fcda02", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "aka47", "type": "User", "id": 7011, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/aka47/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523837a7bd3543c15100fea4"}, "id": 14622316, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3329"}
